&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8f76fc5d-c75f-48ad-9dc6-62b2c316e5ff&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8f76fc5d-c75f-48ad-9dc6-62b2c316e5ff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_60a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
